  <verse number="16" style="v" />For the Lord himself will descend from heaven. He will come with a shout, with the voice of the archangel, and with the trumpet of God, and the dead in Christ will rise first.

  <verse number="17" style="v" />Then we who are alive, who are left, will together with them be caught up in the clouds to meet the Lord in the air. In this way we will always be with the Lord.

  <verse number="18" style="v" />Therefore, comfort one another with these words.</para>
